      "id": "anti-patterns-solutions",
      "title": "⚠️ Anti-patterns & Solutions",
      "description": "Identifier et corriger les mauvaises pratiques",
      "tags": ["anti-patterns", "problèmes", "solutions", "amélioration"],
      "icon": "fas fa-bug",
      "content": "Catalogue des anti-patterns courants et solutions",
